    <text type="letter">
        <body>
           
            <p>Harry,<ptr target="loc.04016_n1"/> I shall come down on Wednesday in the 4 p m train (as I said)&#8212;Nothing new&#8212;I am well&#8212;I had a good day yesterday (Sunday) perfect day&#8212;went over to late breakfast to the Steamer <hi rend="italic">Whillden</hi>, Arch Street wharf<ptr target="loc.04016_n2"/>&#8212;every thing jolly and plentiful &#38; sailor-like&#8212;there four hours&#8212;then in the evening to <choice><abbr>Col:</abbr><expan>Colonel</expan></choice> Johnston's family<ptr target="loc.04016_n3"/>&#8212;I have got your blue flannel shirts for you&#8212;</p>

            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">W W</signed>
            </closer>
            
            <postscript>
                <p>&#8212;love to your father &#38; mother&#8212;</p>
            </postscript> 
        </body>
